50|$|Precision gobs {{can be used}} as preforms for the {{production}} of aspherical lenses in a precision molding process. They are manufactured from a continuous <b>glass</b> <b>melting</b> process. The resulting precision gobs exhibit a very smooth firepolished surface with an excellent surface roughness and high volume accuracy.|$|E
